@startuml Sequence_Admin_Notifications
title Quản Trị - Quản Lý Thông Báo

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant NotificationService as "Notification\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Thông Báo ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Thông báo"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/admin/notifications?page=0&size=20
NotificationService -> Database: Query thong_bao
Database --> NotificationService: Return list
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Notifications list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

== Xem Chi Tiết Thông Báo ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click vào thông báo
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/admin/notifications/{notificationId}
NotificationService -> Database: Get notification details
Database --> NotificationService: Details
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Full info
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết

== Tạo Thông Báo Tin Tức ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Tạo thông báo"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show announcement form
Admin -> FrontEnd: Nhập tiêu đề & nội dung
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: POST /api/admin/announcements\n(title, content)
NotificationService -> Database: Create announcement
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Send to all users
NotificationService -> Database: Create thong_bao for each user
Database --> NotificationService: OK
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Sent
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Gửi thông báo thành công

== Xem Lịch Sử Thông Báo ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Lịch sử"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/admin/announcements?page=0&size=20
NotificationService -> Database: Query announcements
Database --> NotificationService: Return list
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: History list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị lịch sử

== Xem Log Hoạt Động ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Log hoạt động"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: GET /api/admin/audit-logs?page=0&size=20
NotificationService -> Database: Query audit logs
Database --> NotificationService: Log data
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: Logs list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem ai làm gì, khi nào

@enduml
